name: Realital Metaverse
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
"RETA is the governance token of the ‘Reta Wars’ running on the BSC chain. 
RETA token holders can trade for NFT, or hold them for investment purposes. 
Alternatively, you can stake the tokens to get a portion of the fees generated by the game."
